@startuml SD04_Create_Post
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
title SD-04: Create Post (Sync + Async Events)

actor "User" as U
participant "Astro\nFrontend" as FE
participant "Envoy\nGateway" as GW
participant "Spam\nDetection" as SPAM
participant "Post\nService" as POST
database "pg-post\n(sharded)" as DB
queue "Kafka" as KAFKA
participant "Search\nService" as SEARCH
participant "Notification\nService" as NOTIF
database "Meilisearch" as MEILI

U -> FE : Write post (title, body, community)
FE -> GW : POST /api/posts\n{title, body, community_id}\n+ JWT in header
GW -> GW : Validate JWT
GW -> GW : Rate limit (5 posts/hour)

== Synchronous: Spam Check + Save ==
GW -> SPAM : gRPC CheckContent()
SPAM -> SPAM : Keyword blocklist\nURL reputation\nDuplicate detection\nAccount age check
alt Content flagged
    SPAM --> GW : REJECTED (reason)
    GW --> FE : 422 Unprocessable
    FE --> U : "Post rejected: [reason]"
else Content clean
    SPAM --> GW : APPROVED
    GW -> POST : gRPC CreatePost()
    POST -> POST : Hash community_id\n-> select shard
    POST -> DB : INSERT into correct shard
    POST --> GW : 201 Created {post_id}
    GW --> FE : JSON {post_id, url}
    FE --> U : Redirect to new post
end

== Asynchronous: Kafka Fan-Out ==
POST ->> KAFKA : Publish "PostCreated"\n{post_id, community_id, author}
KAFKA ->> SEARCH : Consume event
SEARCH -> MEILI : Index post
KAFKA ->> NOTIF : Consume event
NOTIF -> NOTIF : Find community followers
NOTIF -> NOTIF : Push via WebSocket\n(if online)
KAFKA ->> SPAM : Consume event
SPAM -> SPAM : Post-publish analysis\n(pattern detection)
@enduml
